    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 10th level, you gain the ability to consult with your ancestral spirits. When you do so, you cast the @UUID[Compendium.renegados-compendium.magias.Item.FRcjr28iyZEa13x8] or @UUID[Compendium.renegados-compendium.magias.Item.rlWCBGq8NkfpBJCZ] spell, without using a spell slot or material components. Rather than creating a spherical sensor, this use of @UUID[Compendium.renegados-compendium.magias.Item.rlWCBGq8NkfpBJCZ] invisibly summons one of your ancestral spirits to the chosen location. Wisdom is your spellcasting ability for these spells.</p><p>After you cast either spell in this way, you can't use this feature again until you finish a short or long rest.</p></div>",
